it]], [[Indianapolis International Airport|Indianapolis]], [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Akron\u2013Canton Airport|Akron/Canton]], [[Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport|Baltimore]], [[Logan International Airport|Boston]], [[Cleveland Hopkins International Airport|Cleveland]], [[John Glenn Columbus International Airport|Columbus\u2013Glenn]], [[Bradley International Airport|Hartford]], [[Arnold Palmer Regional Airport|Latrobe/Pittsburgh]], [[Minneapolis\u2212Saint Paul International Airport|Minneapolis/St. Paul]], [[Philadelphia International Airport|Philadelphia]], [[Pittsburgh International Airport|Pittsburgh]] | <ref name=\"SpiritRoutes\">{{cite web|title=Spirit Airlines - Route Map|url=https://www.spirit.com/RouteMaps.aspx|website=www.spirit.com|accessdate=19 February 2017|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223042503/https://www.spirit.com/routemaps.aspx|archive-date=December 23, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| {{nowrap|[[Sun Country Airlines]]}} | [[Minneapolis\u2212Saint Paul International Airport|Minneapolis/St. Paul]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Dane County Regional Airport|Madison]], [[St. Louis Lambert International Airport|St. Louis]] | <ref>{{cite web |title=Route Map & Flight Schedule |url=https://www.suncountry.com/Explore/Route-Map.html |accessdate=19 February 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815090927/https://www.suncountry.com/Explore/Route-Map.html |archive-date=August 15, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[United Airlines]] | [[O'Hare International Airport|Chicago\u2013O'Hare]], [[Denver International Airport|Denver]], [[George Bush Intercontinental Airport|Houston\u2013Intercontinental]], [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Cleveland Hopkins International Airport|Cleveland]], [[Washington Dulles International Airport|Washington\u2013Dulles]]  | <ref name=\"UnitedRoutes\">{{cite web|title=Timetable|url=https://www.united.com/web/en-US/apps/travel/timetable/default.aspx|accessdate=19 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128165254/https://www.united.com/web/en-US/apps/travel/timetable/default.aspx|archive-date=January 28, 2017|url-status=live}}.</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[United Express]] | '''Seasonal:''' [[Cleveland Hopkins International Airport|Cleveland]], [[Washington Dulles International Airport|Washington\u2013Dulles]]| <ref name=\"UnitedRoutes\" />\n<!-- -->\n| [[WestJet]] | [[Toronto Pearson International Airport|Toronto\u2013Pearson]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Ottawa Macdonald\u2013Cartier International Airport|Ottawa]] | <ref name=\"WestJetRoutes\">{{cite web|title=Route map - WestJet.com|url=https://www.westjet.com/en-ca/travel-info/flight-info/route-map|website=www.westjet.com|accessdate=19 February 2017|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220013625/https://www.westjet.com/en-ca/travel-info/flight-info/route-map|archive-date=February 20, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n}}\n\n{| class=\"collapsible collapsed\" style=\"border:1px #aaa solid; width:50em; margin:0.2em auto\"\n|-\n! Domestic Destinations map\n|-\n|{{Location map+ |United_States |width=1300 |float=center\n|caption=Domestic destinations from Southwest Florida International Airport <br /> ({{font color | red | Red}}) = Year-round Destination <br />({{font color | green | Green }}) = Seasonal Destination <br /> ({{font color | blue | Blue }}) = Future Destination\n|places=\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=26.5337 |long=-81.7553 |position=right |label=<div style=\"position:relative; top:-5px;\"><small>'''Fort Myers'''</small></div>|caption=|mark=Airplane_silhouette.svg|marksize=15 }}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=41.0683 |long=-73.7087 |position=left |label=<small>'''{{nowrap|[[Westchester County Airport|White Plains]]}}'''<small>|label_size=100 |marksize=7}}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Green pog.svg |United_States |lat=30.4131 |long=-89.0728 |position=left |label=<small>'''{{nowrap|[[Gulfport-Biloxi International Airport|Gulfport]]}}'''<small>|label_size=100 |marksize=7}}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=43.1391 |long=-89.3364 |position=left |label=<small>'''{{nowrap|[[Dane County Regional Airport|Madison]]}}'''<small>|label_size=100 |marksize=7}}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=40.9154 |long=-81.4419 |position=left |label=<small>'''{{nowrap|[[Akron-Canton Airport|Akron-Canton]]}}'''<small>|label_size=100 |marksize=7}}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Green pog.svg |United_States |lat=40.7948|long=-73.1006|position=right|label='''<small>{{nowrap|[[Long Island MacArthur Airport|Long Island/Islip]]}}</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Green pog.svg |United_States |lat=43.6465|long=-70.3097|position=right|label='''<small>[[Portland International Jetport|Portland]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Green pog.svg |United_States |lat=43.1139|long=-76.1102|position=right|label='''<small>[[Syracuse Hancock International Airport|Syracuse]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=35.213889|long=-80.943056 |position=under |label='''<small>[[Charlotte Douglas International Airport|Charlotte]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=42.948143|long=-87.902010 |position=right|label='''<small>[[Milwaukee International Airport|Milwaukee]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Green pog.svg |United_States |lat=42.934812|long=-78.731318 |position=left|label='''<small>[[Buffalo Niagara International Airport|Buffalo]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |mark = Blue pog.svg |United_States |lat=38.952746|long=-77.457226 |position=left|label='''<small>[[Washington Dulles International Airport|Washington\u2013Dulles]]</small>'''|label_size=80 |marksize=7 }}\n{{Location map~ |United_States |lat=38.851047|long=-77.040320 |position=right|label=