ines]] | [[Hartsfield\u2013Jackson Atlanta International Airport|Atlanta]], [[Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport|Baltimore]], [[Chicago Midway International Airport|Chicago\u2013Midway]], [[John Glenn Columbus International Airport|Columbus\u2013Glenn]], [[Indianapolis International Airport|Indianapolis]], [[Pittsburgh International Airport|Pittsburgh]], [[Lambert\u2013St. Louis International Airport|St. Louis]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Albany International Airport|Albany]], [[Buffalo Niagara International Airport|Buffalo]], [[Cleveland Hopkins International Airport|Cleveland]], [[Dallas Love Field|Dallas-Love]], [[Denver International Airport|Denver]], [[Gerald R. Ford International Airport|Grand Rapids]], [[Bradley International Airport|Hartford]], [[Kansas City International Airport|Kansas City]], [[Milwaukee Mitchell International Airport|Milwaukee]], [[Minneapolis\u2212Saint Paul International Airport|Minneapolis/St. Paul]], [[Nashville International Airport|Nashville]], [[T. F. Green Airport|Providence]], [[Greater Rochester International Airport|Rochester]] | <ref name=\"SouthwestRoutes\">{{cite web|title=Check Flight Schedules|url=https://www.southwest.com/air/flight-schedules/index.html|accessdate=19 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202053931/https://www.southwest.com/air/flight-schedules/index.html|archive-date=February 2, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref> \n<!-- -->\n| [[Spirit Airlines]] | [[Atlantic City International Airport|Atlantic City]], [[O'Hare International Airport|Chicago\u2013O'Hare]], [[Detroit Metropolitan Airport|Detroit]], [[Indianapolis International Airport|Indianapolis]], [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark]]<br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Akron\u2013Canton Airport|Akron/Canton]], [[Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport|Baltimore]], [[Logan International Airport|Boston]], [[Cleveland Hopkins International Airport|Cleveland]], [[John Glenn Columbus International Airpor