 Wadsworth|access-date= 5 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1265492|desc= Latham Farmhouse and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 3 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1265491|desc= Milestone opposite junction with Crimsworth Lane, Wadsworth|access-date= 4 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227389|desc= Plumpton Farmhouse, Wadsworth|access-date= 5 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1226999|desc= South Shields Farmhouse and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 5 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227401|desc= Nos. 1\u20136 Green End and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 4 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227302|desc= No. 1 Old Town Hall Cottages, Wadsworth|access-date= 4 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227400|desc= Nos. 1\u20135 Wainsgate Lane, Wadsworth|access-date= 1 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227292|desc= Boston Hill Cottages, Wadsworth|access-date= 2 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1235132|desc= Bridge at Holme Ends over Alcomden Water, Wadsworth|access-date= 2 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1226828|desc= Clough, Wadsworth|access-date= 2 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1235127|desc= Club Houses, Wadsworth|access-date= 2 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1226980|desc= Coppy Farmhouse and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 2 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1265510|desc= Gib Farmhouse, Wadsworth|access-date= 3 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1265200|desc= Holme Ends Farmhouse and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 3 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227005|desc= New Delight, Wadsworth|access-date= 4 April 2020|mode=cs2|fewer-links=yes}}\n*{{NHLE |num= 1227366|desc= Over Wood Farmhouse and attached barn, Wadsworth|access-date= 4 April 2020|mode=cs2|few